Package: luneos-session
Version: 1.2.0
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: LuneOS Team <luneos@webosports.org>
Depends: luna-surfacemanager, luna-surfacemanager-conf, luna-service2-utils, libluna-service2, systemd
Conflicts: gdm3, lightdm, sddm
Description: LuneOS Session Configuration Bundle
 Comprehensive configuration package for LuneOS on Ubuntu. Includes:
 - All luna-service2 security configs (roles, manifests, permissions)
 - Systemd service files for LuneOS daemons
 - Palm/webOS /etc configuration files
 - Display manager replacement (masks GDM, enables luna-surfacemanager)
 - Automatic user addition to luneos group
 - Fixes for Ubuntu compatibility (bash shebang for surface-manager.sh)
